extendedInfo.description: The Atlantic County Library System in Your Hands!You can now access the Atlantic County Library System anywhere with our latest app! Search for books, movies, audiobooks, music, and more. Just type the first couple letters of words and see the search in action while you type. Manage your account, place holds and renew your items (as long as they are not overdue) from any mobile device. Even checking out eBooks and downloadable audiobooks is made easy! Check out our calendar of events and find our branch locations and hours quickly with the click of a button.Have a question while youâre on the go? Ask a Librarian or connect with us on our social media pages such as Facebook and Twitter. Take the Atlantic County Library System with you!
